by smnandre at 2023-12-18T18:44:46Z

This seems to work now with dedicated entrypoint "extending" app.js

```js
// app-svelte.js
import {registerSvelteControllerComponents} from '@symfony/ux-svelte';

import './app.js';

registerSvelteControllerComponents();
```

--

Info/note:

We could also compose things, like that:

```twig
{% extends 'packageBase.html.twig' %}

{% block importmap %}
    {{ importmap(['app', 'app-react']) }}
{% endblock %}
```

```js
// app-react.js

import {registerReactControllerComponents} from '@symfony/ux-react';

registerReactControllerComponents();
```
